{
  "texts": [
    "ImageClef-VQA-2019 18 is a VQA dataset constructed based on images from MedPix 21.",
    "It comprises 4200 radiological images accompanied by 15,292 question-answer pairs.",
    "These questions are categorized into four types: modality, plane, organ system, and abnormality.",
    "We follow the official dataset split for our evaluation.",
    "Proposed PMC-VQA dataset."
  ]
}